@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant "RouteController" as Ctrl
participant "GetTotalNetworkDistanceUseCase" as UC
participant "RouteRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

ATCC -> Ctrl : GET /api/routes/total-distance
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> UC : execute()
activate UC

UC -> Repo : findByActiveTrue()
activate Repo
Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM routes WHERE is_active = true
activate DB
DB --> Repo : list of active routes
deactivate DB
Repo --> UC : List<Route>
deactivate Repo

note right of UC: For each Route, extracts distance\nfrom its current RouteVersion.\nSums all distances to compute total.

UC --> Ctrl : TotalNetworkDistanceResponse(totalDistanceKm, routeCount)
deactivate UC

Ctrl --> ATCC : 200 OK (JSON Response)
deactivate Ctrl
@enduml
